messages.message: Hey team, if my customer wants to use Aihub on the public site, but has plans to have a Single tenant Aihub commercial when it’s ready. Can we transfer their docs and any apps they’ve built from Aihub to their ST AiHub?

I’m not 100% certain, someone else might be able to confirm.

• Moving docs over will be simple if they mount their own storage to both. 
• I don’t think there a plans to be able to migrate projects, but someone else might be able to confirm.
I'm interested in the answer to this, as well. We have partners who'd like to build apps in their own instance and then provide them to clients in their own instances.

+1 to what Lee said - moving docs and apps is easy to do across environments

cc @hannah on any plans to migrate AI Hub projects
Right now we don't have anything planned to support project migration across environments, but let us look into this further for you.
